latestIgtvVideos.title: Completed 1 year in TMKOC! ❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
27/08/2019

The day I can never forget! 🌸
I remember, was sitting with my family in our living room, waiting for my entry in TMKOC at 8:30pm, Aur phir Malhari song par entry hui, & trust me, I’ve never seen my dad happier than this day, In fact my whole family, it was like a dream come true for me. 🌈✨

Today I would like to thank a few people, because without them, this journey wouldn’t have been possible. 

Firstly, Thank you Asit sir for giving me this golden opportunity, thank you Sohail bhai for believing in me since the day I met you, Thank you @malavrajda for being there by my side since day 1, Ye aapke bina possible nahi hota. 😘

Thank you aai baba @jsonalika @realmandarchandwadkar mujhe itna saara pyaar dene ke liye. 💞

Thank you @maakasamdilipjoshi 
For being the best, watching you perform live is one of the most wonderful experiences of my life.💫

Thank you my dosti gang @_kushah @samayshah_5 @iamazharshaikh for taking care of me. 💛

Thank you @hasmukhi @jennifer_mistry_bansiwal @officialsharadsankla19 @nirmalsoni1 @tan_mahashabde @sodhi_gcs @monika_bhadoriya @jatin.bajaj @dipikas31 @ronakbhavsar2005 for giving me so many beautiful memories. ✨

Precisely, Thank you to the whole cast and crew of the show.🙏🏻❤️

And last but the most important, Thank you Audience for accepting me & for showering so much love since the beginning of my journey, aapke pyaar aur support ke bina ye ek saal ki journey mere liye adhuri hoti, so thank you so much dil se! 🥰🌸

I promise I’ll try my best to entertain you guys!
Keep loving, keep supporting!
Love you all. 🌈♾💖
.
.
.
#gratitudepost #oneyearcompleted

latestIgtvVideos.title: बदलाव ।
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
They say “Be willing to fight for change “ but that fight should start from within, there are so many problems which prevails in our society, in fact we face so many challenges in our life on a daily basis, from having a financial problem at home to not being treated equally to racism to ragging and the list goes on..
But we often forget to use a different lense to look at the same problem. So @samayshah_5 and I tried to put it out there with this write up, and we’ll leave it here for you people to understand what point we were trying to make and how a different approach can altogether change the depth of these problems. 
So here’s presenting “बदलाव” , Hope you guys like it, please let us know your feedback in the comment section below. 
Sending Lots of love & positivity your way!❤️🌸 .
.
.
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy Mother’s Day! ❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Few days back, my mom told me you’ve changed, you don’t dance with me anymore, you’ve stopped teaching me new steps as you used to when you were in school, so I felt really bad and immediately I asked her, would you like to dance with me? Without any hesitation she got up and we started dancing on this song, luckily we had manage to capture this impromptu video, Also I would like to mention my dear friend @kanishkaaaa as she encouraged me to put this up, so here it is! 🙈  I think All of us are guarded by the most powerful of all the angels - Our mother and for all they’ve done for us and they are still doing, we don’t need a special day to celebrate them, if you ask me everyday is Mother’s Day, so whenever you get a chance to make her happy, to tell her that you love her the most, Do it because trust me you’re lucky to have her by your side! ❤️🌈 Happy Mother’s Day mommy!
With love from the luckiest daughter in the world. 👩‍👧🥰 .
.
.
.
#mothersday #videooftheday #loveyou #blessed #actor #palaksidhwani #motherdaughter #happymothersday #instagood #instadaily #love #grateful

latestIgtvVideos.title: मनमर्ज़ी
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
दिल से की हुई छोटी सी कोशिश आप सबके लिए, पसंद आए तो बताना ज़रूर और नहीं आए तो भी बताना| 🙇🏼‍♀️
ढेर सारा प्यार देने के लिए शुक्रिया| ❤️ .
.
.
.

ख़ुदगर्ज़ तो तू भी है.. मैं भी हूँ,
परेशान तू भी है.. मैं भी हूँ,
सपने जो देखे थे आज अचानक बड़े से लगने लगे,
मनचाही राह पर चलते हुए जाने क्यूँ ये पैर डगमगाने लगे,
भीड़ में खड़े हुए नाकामयाबी की परछाई नज़र आयी..
फिर पंख जो खुले थे धीरे धीरे सिमटने लगे.. पर आईने के सामने खड़े जब उन आँखों पर ग़ौर किया..
देखा कि वो फिर से कुछ नए सपने सजाए बैठी है..
नाकामयाबी की परछाई को भूलाए बैठी है,
फिर से एक नई उड़ान भरने की ख़्वाहिश जगी है,
मनमर्ज़ी से जीने की आदत जो लगी है। 💫 .
.

Edit - @callme_shrey Thank you for helping me at the last minute shrey. ❤️
.

My dream of experiencing the Northern Lights came true last month. I couldn’t believe it at first and needed some time to process that it had actually happened. 
We spent 3-4 hours chasing the lights but couldn’t see them because the sky was too cloudy(last two photos), However, I had this feeling that if I had made it this far, the universe wouldn’t let me leave without fulfilling my dream. Then, two days later, while having dinner, I overheard people saying the aurora was visible. I rushed outside, and there it was, right in front of my eyes. 🥹✨
It felt like a beautiful reminder of the power of the universe – that sometimes, all you need is faith, and the universe will reveal its magic. I’m beyond grateful.♥️
 Thank you, Universe.
 Your Favourite Child 
  Palak🧚🏼‍♀️🧿
